The paper deals with medical image analysis using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses image compression techniques, which can be related to information theory (cs.IT) and data compression (cs.DC). Finally, the paper proposes a new compression framework using deep learning, which can be related to machine learning (cs.LG).
